end服务的context canceled错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"conversion request failed: RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded (currencyservice-2)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务因currencyservice故障而无法完成货币转换操作，出现大量context canceled错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to convert currency: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice存在PluginLoader加载问题，可能影响服务稳定性\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http of module http\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"在异常初期出现connection refused错误，表明currencyservice可能经历了重启或网络连接问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n1. **主要根因**：currencyservice服务出现严重的JavaScript堆栈溢出错误（Maximum call stack size exceeded），这可能是由于代码中的递归调用或无限循环导致\n2. **影响范围**：所有frontend实例都受到影响，无法进行货币转换操作\n3. **时间线**：异常从23:10开始，初期有connection refused错误，随后大量出现堆栈溢出错误\n4. **建议后续调查**：需要检查currencyservice的代码逻辑，特别是货币转换相关的递归调用", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的追踪数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是发现的关键异常情况：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"currencyservice->connection_refused\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Currency服务出现连接拒绝错误：'dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused'，导致前端和结账服务无法调用货币转换功能\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService/Convert操作延迟异常激增：正常平均2.3秒，异常时段平均达到15.5秒（延迟倍数6,600倍），表明服务严重超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService/PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常15.4秒增加到71.1秒（延迟倍数4,600倍），受CurrencyService故障影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务HTTP 500错误频发（出现次数：57/55/53），主要由于CurrencyService不可用导致货币转换失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **根因服务**: CurrencyService是问题的核心，出现连接拒绝错误（端口7000无法连接）\n2. **影响传播**: CurrencyService故障导致前端和结账服务的货币转换功能失败\n3. **延迟激增**: CurrencyService的Convert操作延迟增加6,600倍，CheckoutService的PlaceOrder延迟增加4,600倍\n4. **错误状态**: 大量context canceled和HTTP 500错误，表明上游服务因下游超时而取消请求\n\n这明显是一个CurrencyService不可用导致的级联故障，需要进一步检查CurrencyService的健康状态和网络连接。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对监控数据的全面扫描，我发现了显著的异常调用链。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"timeout\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"响应时间急剧恶化，rrt从12057ms飙升至1227598ms，rrt_max达到60001650ms，同时server_error_ratio和error_ratio显著上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt: 12057.58 → 1227598.59 (变化率1.9611), rrt_max: 248913.5 → 60001650.0 (变化率1.9835), error_ratio: 0.0 → 2.03\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"响应时间严重异常，rrt从12145ms增长到1040802ms，rrt_max达到60001799ms，错误率显著上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt: 12145.66 → 1040802.77 (变化率1.9539), rrt_max: 232664.5 → 60001799.0 (变化率1.9845), error_ratio: 0.0 → 1.71\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"最大响应时间异常飙升，rrt_max从225790ms增长到60001629ms，同时响应时间和错误率显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 225790.5 → 60001629.0 (变化率1.985), rrt: 12178.04 → 837742.06 (变化率1.9427), error_ratio: 0.0 → 1.37\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"错误率急剧上升，error_ratio和client_error_ratio均从0%上升到50%，表明服务出现严重故障\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0 → 50.0 (变化率2.0), client_error_ratio